<article>
   <!-- All content will belong in the left-side column -->
   <div class="col-left">
      <div class="section">
         <h2 class="section-header">
            <strong>Our Story</strong>
         </h2>
         <br />
         <p>
            &emsp;&emsp;
            Madison and Neil met at Reedemer Christian High.
            After a year of getting to know each other, they began dating, and slowly fell in love.
            After high school, they both took a gap year to save up for College.
            Now that College is nearly over, Neil and Madison have decided to finally tie the knot after nearly 5 wonderful years.
         </p>
      </div>
      <div class="section">
         <h2 class="section-header">
            <strong>Location</strong>
         </h2>
         <br />
         <p>
            &emsp;&emsp;
            The venue will be held at Equinelle Golf Club in Kemptville, Ontario.
            Please see the map below for directions.
            <div class="mapouter">
               <div class="gmap_canvas">
                  <iframe width="500" height="350" id="gmap_canvas" src="https://maps.google.com/maps?q=140%20Equinelle%20Drive%20K0G%201J0%20Kemptville&t=&z=13&ie=UTF8&iwloc=&output=embed" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" marginheight="0" marginwidth="0"></iframe>
                  <style>
                     .mapouter{position:relative;text-align:right;height:350px;width:500px;}
                     .gmap_canvas {overflow:hidden;background:none!important;height:350px;width:500px;}
                  </style>
               </div>
            </div>
         </p>
      </div>
   </div>
   <!-- All content will belong in the right-side column -->
   <div class="col-right">
      <div class="section">
         <h2 class="section-header">
            <strong>FAQ</strong>
         </h2>
         <br />
         <p>
            <strong>Q: Are children able to attend</strong><br />
            A: Unfortunately, children are not invited to the ceremony or reception unless an exception was explicitely granted.<br />
            <strong>Q: Will people with special dietary needs be accomodated?</strong><br />
            A: Yes, but please notify us in advance if you have any dietary restrictions that ought to be considered.
         </p>
      </div>
   </div>
</article>
